d to the contemplative life."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. Martha Ellice was born in 1385, in England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with Sir John Ellis."},"et":{"1385–":"1385–Surnud","1355–Male":"1355–Surnud","1380–1480":"1380–1480","1385–Female":"1385–Surnud","1355":"1355","1385":"1385","1480":"1480","1380":"1380","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1385–":"1385–Kuollut","1355–Male":"1355–Kuollut","1380–1480":"1380–1480","1385–Female":"1385–Kuollut","1355":"1355","1385":"1385","1480":"1480","1380":"1380","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1385–":"1385–Décédée","1355–Male":"1355–Décédé","1380–1480":"1380–1480","1385–Female":"1385–Décédée","1355":"1355","1385":"1385","1480":"1480","1380":"1380","England, United Kingdom":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Martha Ellice est née en 1385, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Sir John Ellis."},"de":{"1385–":"1385–Verstorben","1355–Male":"1355–Verstorben","1380–1480":"1380–1480","1385–Female":"1385–Verstorben","1355":"1355","1385":"1385","1480":"1480","1380":"1380","England, United Kingdom":"England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Martha Ellice wurde 1385 in England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatte mit Sir John Ellis mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1385–":"1385–Desede","1355–Male":"1355–Desede","1380–1480":"1380–1480","1385–Female":"1385–Desede","1355":"1355","1385":"1385","1480":"1480","1380":"1380","England, United Kingdom":"Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1385–":"1385–elhunyt","1355–Male":"1355–elhunyt","1380–1480":"1380–1480","1385–Female":"1385–elhunyt","1355":"1355","1385":"1385","1480":"1480","1380":"1380","England, United Kingdom":"Anglia, United Kingdom"},"id":{"1385–":"1385–Telah Meninggal","1355–Male":"1355–Telah Meninggal","1380–1480":"1380–1480","1385–Female":"1385–Telah Meninggal","1355":"1355","1385":"1385","1480":"1480","1380":"1380","England, United Kingdom":"Inggris, United Kingdom"},"it":{"